title: Hypnosis. Gerald kein-Eliminating Sugar Addiction
description:
Fifty years ago Diabetes was a negligible problem. The percentages of increased heart disease in both men and women has dramatically risen! The cause of many mental illnesses can be directly traced to excessive sugar intake. Sugar consumption is the major culprit to our declining physical and mental health.

In this training, you will discover Jerry's unique and specific techniques for educating the client concerning the negative effects of sugar.  He combines these techniques with step-by-step instruction methods for the removal of this powerful addiction from your clients life.
